<statement>
<p>Solve the equation: <m>\displaystyle{15}{\left({10}^{{-{3}{x}}}\right)}-{2}={0}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}=</m><input type="text" style="width:8.2ch" name="qn0" id="qn0" value="" autocomplete="off" aria-label="Question 1" class="text"/> </p>
<p>Round to 3 decimal places.</p>

</statement>
<solution>
<p><ul><li>0.292</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{15}{\left({10}^{{-{3}{x}}}\right)}-{2}={0}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{15}{\left({10}^{{-{3}{x}}}\right)}=-{2}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{10}^{{-{3}{x}}}=-\frac{{2}}{{15}}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{3}{x}={\log{{\left(-\frac{{2}}{{15}}\right)}}}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}=\frac{{\log{{\left(-\frac{{2}}{{15}}\right)}}}}{{-{{3}}}}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}\approx{0.292}</m></p>
</solution>
